{"tid":906424,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【又入波】休班警員涉非禮16歲女被捕","createTime":"2018-11-18T03:42:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T19:54:46.000Z","uid":54337,"like":131,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"4740b9ad80b939cc1e5f742c44d152d8ebe03516","tid":906424,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T03:42:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.best-gif.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/funny-gifs-Goaaaaaaaaaaal-Goal-Goal-Goal-Goal-Goaaaaaal.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.best-gif.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F02%2Ffunny-gifs-Goaaaaaaaaaaal-Goal-Goal-Goal-Goal-Goaaaaaal.gif&h=55e4bb11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n休班警員涉非禮16歲女被捕<br />\n11月17日(六) 21:40<br />\n<br />\n警方在昨早(16日)約8時，接獲一名16歲女童報案，指懷疑在港鐵荔景站被非禮，警方接報派員聲至，經初步調查後，警方以涉嫌非禮，拘捕一名姓趙(54歲)男子，並證實他為一名休班警務人員。趙其後獲准保釋候查，須於12月中旬向警方報到，案件由葵青警區重案組跟進。<br />\n<br />\n警方重申，警隊非常重視人員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，警隊絕不容忍和姑息，定必嚴正處理，進行刑事調查及紀律覆檢。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181117/mobile/bkn-20181117214045158-1117_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181117%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20181117214045158-1117_00822_001.html&d=LeNpBdcj6I5QCBKhB5VE%2BZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=b69cbf82\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181117/mobile/bkn-20181117214045158-1117_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"8e8435e8407fd61098dc56fafa09e8f2d9439dd1","tid":906424,"uid":92512,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T03:43:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f2b6ca8791e2d90cedf0720708ba70c3af415e3","tid":906424,"uid":54337,"like":74,"dislike":1,"score":73,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T03:43:16.000Z","msg":"Ol&eacute; Ol&eacute; Ol&eacute;<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/as